---Lynxiz---

Lynxiz looks at Termitron, "Termitron, you have that, that homesick 
sort of look about you." She looks at him thinking, her snowy fur 
tipped ears twitch, then she turns to Alpha Dolphy. "I'm pretty sure 
that Termitron is homesick for where ever he was before he helped 
me reach the Starjumper... maybe we should get him back to, to 
where he came from, where ever that was again... Termitron? 
Where were you from again?"
